OL,5, The Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency
OL,6, (DVLA) has been accused of "recklessly"
OL,7, telling staff to work in its Swansea HQ
OL,8, after the central heating broke.       
OL,10,FLaura Bee, of the Public and Commercial
OL,11,FServices (PCS) union, said they have no
OL,12,Fhot water in toilets and were told to  
OL,13,Fwear more clothes.                     
OL,15,FThe DVLA said staff who feel           
OL,16,F"uncomfortable" can work from home or  
OL,17,Ffrom another building.                 
OL,19,FMs Bee also said temperatures dropped  
OL,20,Fbelow 11C (52F) in the building.       
